notes.text: Associate Devyn Rodriguez claims that suspect was eating a table at the time of the crime. If this is true it's really weird.
Micaela Gleason claims that the suspect was defensivly drinking bagels at the time of the crime, however bagels are a solid food.
Associate of Arno claims that he was eating a shoe at the time of the crimes. Do all the criminals in Glassdale insist upon eating things that aren't edible?
